commit b71f37b8
Author: Klaus Ethgen <Klaus@Ethgen.de>
Date:   Sun Feb 28 15:17:12 2010 +0000

    Fix a small issue with strptime
    
    strptime do not initialize all fields. So the undefined fields could end
    in crash later on.

