Date:   Thu Aug 21 22:47:49 2008 +0000

    Replace macros VDLIST_INFO() and VDTREE_INFO() by shorter VDLIST() and VDTREE(). VDLIST_INFO(vd, part) becomes VDLIST(vd)->part.

