Author: Laurent Monin <zas@norz.org>
Date:   Wed Jul 23 17:38:04 2008 +0000

    Minor tidy up.

commit bd26225b
Author: Laurent Monin <zas@norz.org>
Date:   Wed Jul 23 12:46:35 2008 +0000

